title: Bobby’s Fiancé Had An Accident + Lunchbox Teaches His Wife To Drive Stick Shift + Clint And Lisa Black Share Details Of Their Time On 'The Masked Singer'
itunes:title: Bobby’s Fiancé Had An Accident + Lunchbox Teaches His Wife To Drive Stick Shift + Clint And Lisa Black Share Details Of Their Time On 'The Masked Singer'
description:
Bobby talks about how his fiancé Caitlin got hurt yesterday. Lunchbox shares the audio of him teaching his wife to drive a stick shift in an empty parking lot. Plus, we talk to Clint Black and his wife Lisa about their new duet, secrets to a successful marriage and how locked down they were while filming The Masked Singer!
